fileSamples.statement:
(types : list composite_definition) : wf_composites types ->
{ce : composite_env | build_composite_env types = OK ce}.
fileSamples.proofString:
unfold wf_composites.
case (build_composite_env types); intros.
exists c; reflexivity.
contradiction.

fileSamples.statement:
(types : list composite_definition) : match build_composite_env types with
| OK _ => True
| Error _ => False
end -> {ce : composite_env | build_composite_env types = OK ce}.
fileSamples.proofString:
case (build_composite_env types); intros.
exists c; reflexivity.
contradiction.

fileSamples.statement: (types : list composite_definition) (c : composite_env) (WF : True) : {ce : composite_env | OK c = OK ce}.
(types : list composite_definition) (e : errmsg) (WF : False) : {ce : composite_env | Error e = OK ce}.
